itunes:summary:
Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway sit down with Medal Of Honor Recipient Dakota Meyer as we discuss one of the drunkest nights we've ever had together, his regrets on not doing the film Range 15 and why, and the burden he feels being award the Medal Of Honor and the shame he feels.  This is one of the best episodes in the history of our show.
